{"tid":2262861,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強「影帝」上身拍片撐維穩歌自high過戲癮","createTime":"2020-10-29T12:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T13:55:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"181e828b1a3af55d72790402eb4afc6f92a99827","tid":2262861,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AeeaPf6jqiaxfZpHOq29pwGuRR8=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BU7Y62HWLZA5VAD7SVLBIWNTQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAeeaPf6jqiaxfZpHOq29pwGuRR8%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBU7Y62HWLZA5VAD7SVLBIWNTQ4.jpg&h=a889f72f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PLTNfUoNLa7AkrPa_1Ovp7WOFTc=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/32VJUXMKRVBDNFB4STAIBVJ52E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPLTNfUoNLa7AkrPa_1Ovp7WOFTc%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F32VJUXMKRVBDNFB4STAIBVJ52E.jpg&h=fb179a35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A3wr7HIiEuOcRqc9GP-69eTzVhE=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JVHYWDJTW5G7NB3FWQ6KYFXIQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA3wr7HIiEuOcRqc9GP-69eTzVhE%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJVHYWDJTW5G7NB3FWQ6KYFXIQQ.jpg&h=f1ded7ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「被警務生涯耽誤演藝事業」，香港警務處處長「PK鄧」鄧炳強曾揚言自己跟成龍學做警察，又喜歡拖馬跟明星足球隊埋堆，更在今年2月香港最嚴峻的疫情下，跟一眾藝人及警員舉行「撐警無罩宴」，又攬頭攬頸唱K，宴上眾人口沫橫飛，如此高調廣結知己的處長，可謂前無古人，後無來者。<br />\n<br />\n講起做戲，PK鄧曾經做過高薪老臨，黃百鳴也踢爆PK鄧，唔止拍新藝城一部戲，難怪間唔中會身痕過戲癮。今日香港警察官方facebook貼出一條宣傳片，硬sell撐警維穩歌《捍衛香港》，該首歌由鍾鎮濤創作，片中以洗腦式翻loop歌10秒，全程只播幾句，而PK鄧亦粉墨登場。<br />\n<br />\nPK鄧並冇埋沒自己嘅演藝天份，更「影帝」上身，表情多多，為求滿足自己的表演慾，更特登清唱幾句大晒歌喉，PK鄧落力表演都希望有知音人，見該官網FB小編亦刻意阿諛奉承，打tag「處長歌聲令人耳朵懷孕了」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201029/6J75LCJZUVEP5F2U7AAEEOOTO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201029%2F6J75LCJZUVEP5F2U7AAEEOOTO4%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KilUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=9ef55203\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201029%2F6J75LCJZUVEP5F2U7AAEEOOTO4%2F&h=a8c06cb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201029/6J75LCJZUVEP5F2U7AAEEOOTO4/</a>"},{"pid":"3e15155ec139fe868de1c12d41a0042271227554","tid":2262861,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"做署長做到成個PR咁<br />\n無曬威嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba021b7ad07cff440fdd05bb062fd6437d9b12bc","tid":2262861,"uid":53498,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:05:25.000Z","msg":"幾時拍gv,過下戲癮"},{"pid":"d447a1fca8d8068ab8a41a5b4c909bd71c70307e","tid":2262861,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3e15155ec139fe868de1c12d41a0042271227554","tid":2262861,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"做署長做到成個PR咁<br />\n無曬威嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:05:53.000Z","msg":"支共啲宣傳不嬲又柒又老土"},{"pid":"a5787fa212b057ba7b92a8c2db1e69d096343763","tid":2262861,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba021b7ad07cff440fdd05bb062fd6437d9b12bc","tid":2262861,"uid":53498,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:05:25.000Z","msg":"幾時拍gv,過下戲癮"},"citedBy"